ystacks
Copyright 2026 Yesterday

Yesterday's PUBLIC Claude Code plugin catalog. Lists generic-tauglich plugins
(no Yesterday-infra deps). Plus hosts `plugins/ydstack/` as a monorepo subdir.

---

## Listed plugins

Each plugin in the catalog carries its own LICENSE and NOTICE in its respective
repository. Installing a plugin via this catalog fetches it directly from its
upstream source; ystacks does not interpose, modify, or redistribute plugin
code (with the exception of `plugins/ydstack/` which is hosted in this repo).

See `.claude-plugin/marketplace.json` for the authoritative list.

---

## Companion catalog

The private companion catalog `Yesterday-AI/ystacks-internal` hosts
Yesterday-team-internal plugins (clawrag, llm-gateway, paperclip-companies,
etc.) and bundle plugins (yastack-internal, yopstack-internal) that compose
public + internal via cross-marketplace dependencies.

---

## Claude Code

ystacks is a marketplace catalog for Claude Code, a product of Anthropic.
<https://claude.com/code>

The marketplace format and `marketplace.json` schema are part of Claude Code's
public extension API.
